{
  "stem": "17135.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 259.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And then, we were not supposed to hand out that much, but for some reason, I detected-- they call this the prominent-- you remember what prominent means-- the prominenten block.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "It was a block where all the people that worked in the SS officers-- somebody was a, a barber, the other guy was, was a, a typist, the other guy was a bookkeeper, the other guys worked in the-- where they give out uniforms, in the storage, what have you.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They all lived in the separate block.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They were all Germans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "There were very few Poles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And the Lageralteste, which is, which is a very powerful person in the camp, he had sometimes by far more power than his SS sergeant.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Believe me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And he also was manipulating the SS.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "At that time was when they called us anti-social, you had a black triangle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "He wasn't a criminal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Anti-social.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Anti-social was swindlers, people that married women and exploited them, small swindlers, insurance betrayers, all kind of people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And this guy was from Cologne.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "In Germany, each province has its own dialect.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "There's the Bavaria dialect, the Rhenish dialect, a Westphalian dialect, a Saxon dialect, Bavarian dialect, everybody has Thuringian dialect.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And he talked-- he was so primitive that he couldn't even speak Hochdeutsch.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "A real German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "He was talking real like a primitive-- but he was the Lageralteste.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And I saw that this man was constantly looking at his boots.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Yeah, that was also privalege.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "He had, he got boots they took away from a Jewish civilian.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And, and he normally should have gone to, to Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "But he had connections because he was Lageralteste.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "They allowed him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "He wanted boots.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "He got a pair of boots.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And he had boots that were shining like a mirror.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
